OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FITV News' James Mates speaks to
OL,8,FHezbollah politician Hussein Hajj
OL,9,FHassan, who holds both Israel and the
OL,10,FUS responsible for escalation in the
OL,11,FMiddle East
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump and Israel
OL,14,Ftogether are responsible for killing
OL,15,F"thousands and thousands" of people, a
OL,16,Fsenior Hezbollah politician has told
OL,17,FITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
