PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FIn the exclusive interview, Hussein
OL,8,FHajj Hassan said that the recent
OL,9,Fescalation in Lebanon stems from
OL,10,FIsrael's continued military actions in
OL,11,Fthe region.
OL,13,F"The Iranians said, if you attack the
OL,14,Fsouth suburbs of Beirut, Iran will
OL,15,Frespond. So, yesterday, Israel
OL,16,Fattacked the south suburb of Beirut,
OL,17,Fand Iran attacked Israel," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,F"Why? The alliance between the United
OL,8,FStates and Israel is very clear, and
OL,9,FIran is our ally, and they help us,"
OL,10,Fhe added.
OL,12,FHezbollah, an Iran-backed group, has
OL,13,Fbeen involved in the recent conflict
OL,14,Fin the region, which broke out after
OL,15,Fjoint US-Israeli attacks on Iran in
OL,16,FFebruary this year.
OL,18,FIt still holds significant power in
OL,19,FLebanon, despite being weakened by an
OL,20,FIsraeli campaign in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
