PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FOn Monday, Israel and Iran traded fire
OL,8,Fin their first attacks since the US
OL,9,Fstruck a ceasefire with Tehran on
OL,10,FApril 8.
OL,12,FHours later, the Iranian military said
OL,13,Fthat it was halting its offensive
OL,14,Foperations as long as Israel stops its
OL,15,Fattacks on Lebanon.
OL,17,FWhen asked who he believes is in
OL,18,Fcharge ` Trump or Israel ` Hassan
OL,19,Freplied "together".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FOn whether Israel would listen to a
OL,8,Ftheoretical plea from Trump to stop
OL,9,Fattacking Lebanon, Hassan said: "I
OL,10,Fthink they are together responsible
OL,11,Ffor the attack on Lebanon, on
OL,12,FPalestine, and on Iran.
OL,14,F"They are allied", he continued, "they
OL,15,Fassume the responsibility, together".
OL,17,F"Together they are not innocent,
OL,18,Ftogether they are responsible for the
OL,19,Fkilling of thousands and thousands of
OL,20,Fpeople."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
