PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FWhen asked why Hezbollah would not
OL,8,Fjoin the ceasefire agreement made
OL,9,Fbetween the Lebanese government and
OL,10,FIsrael last week, he said "because
OL,11,Fit's a very, very bad agreement".
OL,13,FHe added that, for Hezbollah to agree
OL,14,Fto stop fighting Israeli forces, the
OL,15,Fmilitant group requires "ceasefire
OL,16,Fwithout the liberty of action of
OL,17,FIsrael in Lebanon", and immediate
OL,18,Fwithdrawal from "our territory"
OL,19,F(Lebanon), as well as the "liberation
OL,20,Fof prisoners" and the return of
OL,21,Fdisplaced citizens.
OL,26,@{D@Apm{D@Ipn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
