OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FLebanon's Ministry of Health say that
OL,8,Fbetween March 2, 2026 and June 7,
OL,9,F2026, there have been over 14,600
OL,10,Fcasualties and over 3,600 civilian
OL,11,Fdeaths.
OL,13,FHassan condemned Israeli's nuclear
OL,14,Farsenal and laws permitting the
OL,15,Fexecution of Palestinian prisoners,
OL,16,Fwhich he likened to Nazi practices.
OL,18,F"Peace - that means justice. Peace -
OL,19,Fthat means rights", he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
