PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FHassan also criticised the United
OL,8,FStates for changing its stance on the
OL,9,Fterms of the ceasefire, allegedly
OL,10,Funder Israeli pressure.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"Since April 8 to now, the agreement
OL,18,Fbetween the United States and Iran is
OL,19,Fnot accomplished, because, you know,
OL,20,FTrump has changed his idea everyday
OL,21,Ffive or six times."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
