PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780974217
OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,F"I hope Trump will not change" his
OL,8,Fideas because of the "pressure of the
OL,9,FIsraeli government", he later added.
OL,11,FThe Hezbollah politician further
OL,12,Falleged that the US supplied arms to
OL,13,Fthe Lebanese army not to defend
OL,14,Fagainst Israel but to weaken
OL,15,FHezbollah, a claim he says has gone
OL,16,Funanswered by Lebanese officials.
OL,18,FHassan maintained that Hezbollah will
OL,19,Fnever recognise Israel as a state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
