OL,3,CTrump and Israel 'responsible' for
OL,4,Ckilling thousands, Hezbollah
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FWhen asked if, "in the interest of
OL,8,Fpeace, without recognising it",
OL,9,FHezbollah could live alongside Israel,
OL,10,Fthe aide said "the responsibility of
OL,11,Fthe war in our region is Israel".
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
